Directed by @bhatiaaakash @loudmouth.film

latestPosts.caption:
Self presentation in itself is unreal. Dame Imfala is unreal. They let me warp palpable reality and live through the process of embodying different personalities using fashion as a form of performance. Dame Imfala makes me feel limitless and liberated; it only felt befitting to memorialise my short journey in drag so far to remind myself of the ambiguous possibilities of the art form, with the help of my best Judy @vantagold

With its vast universe and various characters, a Tarot Deck felt like the perfect representation of my drag, as they both symbolise an altered state of consciousness.

🏹 Dame Imfala presents The Chariot 🏹

Last card from the Major Arcana series. This is an ongoing project with @vantagold and we cannot wait to share the rest soon. Watch this space for more!

Design and Illustration @vantagold ✨
Wearing @amit__tete
Make Up Artistry @adventrong

latestPosts.caption:
On the cover of @vogueindia August'22 issue with the queers and my best judy @dameimfala 🏳️‍🌈🏳‍⚧

It’s here, it’s #queer—a resounding, unifying thread that weaves through the stories in @vogueindia 's August issue, which speaks to the inherent need for self-expression and the right to be who one is or wants to be, without the fear of violence. Fashion is a safe space for the #LGBTQIA+ community worldwide and we are proud to shine a spotlight on its fearless and fabulous members via this joyous tribute.

Photographer: Kalpesh Lathigra (@kalpeshlathigra)
